Cedar Avenue Apt. T Burbank, Calif. 91502 15 Please come to the office shown below at the time and place indicated in connection with an official matter. OFFICE LOCATION 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA 90012Room No. 8024 Floor No. 8th DATE AND HOUR MONDAY, FEBRUARY 26, 1979 - 9:30 A.M. ASK FOR Immigration Examiner REASON FOR Interview regarding your form I-130 visa petitions filed in bohalf of: APPOINTMENT Manibhai Shivabhai PATEL and Champa Manibhai PATEL BRING WITH YOU This letter, your citizenship paper and a certified copy of your birth. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU KEEP THIS APPOINTMENT AND BRING THIS LETTER WITH YOU. If you are unable to do so, state your reason, sign below and return this letter to this office at once. I am unable to keep the appointment because: MY PARENTS Very truly yours, HAD LEFT FOR INDIA DUE TO UNAVOIDABLE Jack E. Fortner CIRCUMSTANCES. AT PRESENT THEY DON'T Assistant District Director for WISH TO RESIDE IN UNITED STATES. Travel Control DATE SIGNATURE Parimal M. Patel 2-13-79 Form G-56 (Rev. 5-1-73) N
